title: Did Thristype Retire Ogilve?
content:
Back in September I linked to 'Ogilve' for a Type ID request.

[http://typophile.com/node/61509](http://web.archive.org/web/20140829112349/http:/typophile.com/node/61509 "http://typophile.com/node/61509")
